8
00:00:55,889 --> 00:00:57,432
They're outsiders.

9
00:01:03,521 --> 00:01:05,190
And with interest.

10
00:01:07,817 --> 00:01:09,110
Not just for you,

11
00:01:09,194 --> 00:01:10,653
but for Mikoy too.

12
00:01:22,665 --> 00:01:24,083
Just investigate this.

13
00:01:24,167 --> 00:01:25,585
I'll handle it, sir.

14
00:01:25,668 --> 00:01:27,504
Uh, Dara…

15
00:01:27,587 --> 00:01:28,671
