- Are you okay?

270
00:18:10,506 --> 00:18:13,801
Wow! Wow! Oh, no!

271
00:18:13,884 --> 00:18:17,679
My dear is like… magnificent!
Something like that.

272
00:18:17,763 --> 00:18:20,390
- I just went out with Mikoy.
- Am I right?

273
00:18:20,474 --> 00:18:22,226
You don't need to verbalize it

274
00:18:22,309 --> 00:18:26,271
because I can see
the twinkle in your eyes.

275
00:18:26,355 --> 00:18:27,314
You're laughing?

276
00:18:27,397 --> 00:18:30,776
It's humanizing that
you're spending time with Mikoy.

277
00:18:32,027 --> 00:18:33,195
You know, Mom.

278
00:18:38,367 --> 00:18:40,828
I spent the whole day with him,
and it was just endless

279
00:18:40,911 --> 00:18:43,205
corny pickup lines.

280
00:18:43,288 --> 00:18:47,918
I never thought I'd be able to appreciate
that kind of humor.

281
00:18:50,087 --> 00:18:51,588
Do you know what it's called?

282
00:18:55,008 --> 00:18:56,135
Love.

283
00:18:59,179 --> 00:19:01,640
There. You're happy when you're with him.

284
00:19:05,018 --> 00:19:06,353
Let's not go that far.

285
00:19:07,146 --> 00:19:12,985
How do you think
I survived your dad all these years?

286
00:19:13,068 --> 00:19:14,444
Think about it.

287
00:19:14,528 --> 00:19:16,780
I'm not a patient person.

288
00:19:17,865 --> 00:19:20,325
But when I met him, I learned to…

289
00:19:21,201 --> 00:19:23,537
endure a lot.

290
00:19:26,081 --> 00:19:28,500
Was it easy for you when…

291
00:19:29,835 --> 00:19:32,963
you found out the truth about dad?

292
00:19:33,046 --> 00:19:37,634
That… he's not just
an ordinary businessman?

293
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:47,352
I'm going to sleep now.

294
00:19:48,604 --> 00:19:49,938
Are you sure?

295
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,065
Your hair is still wet.

296
00:19:54,234 --> 00:19:56,570
You might get a headache.

297
00:19:56,653 --> 00:19:58,405
What are you talking about?

298
00:19:58,488 --> 00:20:00,699
You know what? Just go to sleep too.

299
00:20:02,701 --> 00:20:03,744
Here.

300
00:20:04,995 --> 00:20:06,538
Wait, what are you doing?

301
00:20:06,622 --> 00:20:08,916
- Going to sleep.
- No.

302
00:20:08,999 --> 00:20:10,584
Just sleep here beside me.

303
00:20:10,667 --> 00:20:12,377
- Beside you?
- Yes.

304
00:20:12,461 --> 00:20:13,837
Why? Is there a problem?

305
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:15,589
Are you going to take advantage of me?

306
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:16,590
No!

307
00:20:16,673 --> 00:20:18,258
Do you have a girlfriend
who will get jealous?

308
00:20:19,343 --> 00:20:21,178
- None.
- No problem then.

309
00:20:21,261 --> 00:20:22,804
Just sleep here beside me.

310
00:20:22,888 --> 00:20:25,057
So you can sleep comfortably.

311
00:20:29,186 --> 00:20:30,354
I'll just fix this.

312
00:20:49,581 --> 00:20:51,750
What are you waiting for? Go to sleep.

313
00:20:54,086 --> 00:20:55,212
Okay.

314
00:21:02,344 --> 00:21:03,720
Easy?

315
00:21:06,932 --> 00:21:08,642
Dear, with this beauty.

316
00:21:10,769 --> 00:21:11,895
From Mabalacat, Pampanga.

317
00:21:11,979 --> 00:21:15,148
Then I just ended up in a syndicate.

318
00:21:15,232 --> 00:21:16,066
But…

319
00:21:16,984 --> 00:21:18,610
I wanted to run away.

320
00:21:20,904 --> 00:21:22,656
To the point that…

321
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:27,035
I wanted to forget him.

322
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:29,663
I wanted to… I wanted to open my mind,

323
00:21:29,746 --> 00:21:32,165
so I could remove him from my memory.
That he exists.

324
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:34,626
Because I love him.

325
00:21:35,877 --> 00:21:39,131
I can't leave him.
I can't turn away from him.

326
00:21:40,424 --> 00:21:42,634
And I realized that's how it is, my dear.

327
00:21:42,718 --> 00:21:44,678
You'll endure everything.

328
00:21:44,761 --> 00:21:46,179
You'll face everything.

329
00:21:46,763 --> 00:21:48,307
Just for the person you love.

330
00:21:50,809 --> 00:21:52,102
So, my dear,

331
00:21:54,104 --> 00:21:55,897
if Mikoy truly loves you,

332
00:21:55,981 --> 00:21:58,650
he will accept you no matter who you are.

333
00:21:59,401 --> 00:22:01,778
Whoever you may be. Okay?

334
00:22:11,747 --> 00:22:12,831
Who is that?

335
00:22:13,749 --> 00:22:17,461
Chiara Valtrovi. The daughter of Viktor.

336
00:22:18,462 --> 00:22:19,421
And from what it looks like,

337
00:22:19,504 --> 00:22:22,674
it seems the leader of Moraviano
will settle in the country.

338
00:22:23,884 --> 00:22:25,260
And if my sources are correct,

339
00:22:25,343 --> 00:22:28,346
they already bought a mansion in Fourbest.

340
00:22:37,856 --> 00:22:41,276
Do we really need to drag
his daughter into this?

341
00:22:45,113 --> 00:22:48,033
And they have already
crippled our operations!

342
00:22:51,203 --> 00:22:52,829
If we kill his daughter,

343
00:22:52,913 --> 00:22:55,415
it will send a clear
and unmistakable message.

344
00:22:56,333 --> 00:23:00,170
Foreign syndicates are not welcome
in our country.

345
00:23:01,004 --> 00:23:04,800
Only Filipinos are allowed
to deceive fellow Filipinos!

346
00:23:23,693 --> 00:23:28,865
I didn't expect such a big change,
since you just started.

347
00:23:29,449 --> 00:23:31,201
Thank you, sir. But that's nothing.

348
00:23:31,284 --> 00:23:34,079
I just made a few adjustments
to our manpower.

349
00:23:34,162 --> 00:23:36,456
To make our operations more efficient.

350
00:23:36,540 --> 00:23:37,415
That's all.

351
00:23:39,709 --> 00:23:40,669
Wow.

352
00:23:44,339 --> 00:23:45,507
Chiara.

353
00:23:50,011 --> 00:23:53,390
- Papa…
- It would be a pity.

354
00:23:54,182 --> 00:23:56,059
He might become cold.

355
00:23:56,143 --> 00:23:57,185
Hey!

356
00:23:57,269 --> 00:23:59,020
Silly you!

357
00:24:01,148 --> 00:24:03,900
No, we're just happy
with your performance, Mikoy.

358
00:24:03,984 --> 00:24:05,694
Thank you.

359
00:24:05,777 --> 00:24:09,489
I just don't want to disappoint you
with the trust you gave me.

360
00:24:09,573 --> 00:24:12,367
I'll do my best for the company.

361
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:16,204
That's why we already discussed it.

362
00:24:16,288 --> 00:24:18,665
We should have a party.

363
00:24:19,291 --> 00:24:20,542
Something like a celebration!

364
00:24:21,251 --> 00:24:22,961
What? A celebration?

365
00:24:23,962 --> 00:24:25,380
That's not necessary.

366
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:31,469
It's like a welcoming party.

367
00:24:31,553 --> 00:24:33,305
No need for a welcoming party.

368
00:24:33,388 --> 00:24:35,223
I already feel very welcomed.

369
00:24:35,307 --> 00:24:36,850
I feel more welcomed than "Rotonda".

370
00:24:38,059 --> 00:24:39,769
You know what? You're funny!

371
00:24:40,770 --> 00:24:42,105
Without even trying.

372
00:24:42,689 --> 00:24:46,109
You're not the only main character
in this story. Come on.

373
00:24:46,193 --> 00:24:47,611
What Mom is trying to say

374
00:25:00,248 --> 00:25:04,586
It's time for the whole Philippines
to know

375
00:25:04,669 --> 00:25:07,172
the Valtrovi family.

376
00:25:23,021 --> 00:25:24,773
<i>We need to smoke them out.</i>

377
00:25:24,856 --> 00:25:27,359
<i>So we can eliminate those insects.</i>

378
00:25:34,157 --> 00:25:35,659
<i>Just a reminder, Kian.</i>

379
00:25:35,742 --> 00:25:38,870
<i>We are there as undercover agents.</i>
<i>Not to join the party.</i>

380
00:25:54,886 --> 00:25:58,932
But I guess
this is how it feels to hit the jackpot.

381
00:25:59,015 --> 00:25:59,849
Chiara,

382
00:25:59,933 --> 00:26:03,395
I just want you to know
that I will do everything for you.

383
00:26:09,943 --> 00:26:10,944
<i>Viktor!</i>

384
00:26:12,821 --> 00:26:13,947
Mikoy!
